This paper is about Answer Set Programming (ASP), which is a subfield of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper specifically deals with the computation of paracoherent answer sets, which involves nonmonotonic reasoning and logic (cs.LO and cs.PL). The algorithms proposed in the paper also involve data structures and computational complexity (cs.DS and cs.CC).
